Section 6.2.6

F4verl <- subset(verlander, pitch_type == "FF")
F4verl$gameDay <- as.integer(format(F4verl$gamedate, format = "%j"))

dailySpeed <- aggregate(speed ~ gameDay + season, 
                        data = F4verl,
                        FUN = mean)
# time for first plot 

speedFC <- subset(verlander, 
                  pitch_type %in% c("FF" , "CH"))
avgspeedFC <- aggregate( speed ~ pitch_type + season,
                         data = speedFC,
                         FUN = mean)
avgspeedFC <- droplevels(avgspeedFC)
avgspeedFC
##   pitch_type season    speed

# first plot
xyplot(speed ~ gameDay | factor(season),
       data = dailySpeed,
       xlab = "day of the year",
       ylab = "pitch speed (MPH)")

#second plot
dotplot(factor(season) ~ speed,
        group = pitch_type,
        data = avgspeedFC,
        pch = c("C","F"),
        cex = 2)

section 6.2.8

NoHit <- subset(verlander, gamedate == "2011-05-07")

# bulid 3 graphs

pitchnames <- list("change-up",
                  "curveball",
                  "4S-fastball",
                  "2S-fastball",
                  "slider")

myKey <- list(space = "right",
              border = TRUE,
              cex.title = 0.8,
              title = "pitch type",
              text = pitchnames,
              padding.text = 4)

topKzone <- 3.5
botKzone <- 1.6
inKzone <- -0.95
outKzone <- 0.95

# build final graph
xyplot(pz ~ px | batter_hand,
       data = NoHit,
       groups = pitch_type,
       auto.key = TRUE)

xyplot(pz ~ px | batter_hand,
       data = NoHit,
       groups = pitch_type,
       auto.key = TRUE,
       aspect = "iso")

xyplot(pz ~ px | batter_hand,
       data = NoHit,
       groups = pitch_type,
       auto.key = TRUE,
       aspect = "iso",
       xlim = c(-2.2, 2.2),
       ylim = c(0, 5),
       xlab = "Horizontal Location\n(ft. from middle of plate)",
       ylab = "Vertical Loaction\n(ft. from ground)")

# the final plot
xyplot(pz ~ px | batter_hand,
       data = NoHit,
       groups = pitch_type,
       auto.key = TRUE,
       aspect = "iso",
       xlim = c(-2.2, 2.2),
       ylim = c(0, 5),
       xlab = "Horizontal Location\n(ft. from middle of plate)",
       ylab = "Vertical Loaction\n(ft. from ground)",
       panel = function (...){
            panel.xyplot(...)
            panel.rect(inKzone,
                       botKzone,
                       outKzone,
                       topKzone,
                       border = "black",
                       lty = 3)
       })

Section 6.3.9

kZone <- data.frame(
     x = c(inKzone, inKzone, outKzone, outKzone, inKzone),
     y = c(botKzone, topKzone, topKzone, botKzone, botKzone))

ggplot(F4verl, aes(px,pz)) +
     geom_point() +
     facet_wrap(~batter_hand) +
     coord_equal() +
     geom_path(aes(x, y),
               data = kZone,
               lwd = 2,
               col = "white")

ggplot(F4verl, aes(px,pz)) +
     stat_binhex() +
     facet_wrap(~batter_hand) +
     coord_equal() +
     geom_path(aes(x, y),
               data = kZone,
               lwd = 2,
               col = "white",
               alpha = 0.3)
